items.Video_Title: Beautiful Interior Details | Luxury Home Tour
items.Video_Description:
The moment you drive through the gates of 915 Sinclair it feels like you have entered a retreat where all stress and worry disappear. The homes quiet elegant exterior creates an inviting atmosphere from the moment you arrive and belies the beauty that lies within.

Custom built with over 7000 sf on three levels sitting on a stunning “park like” .38 acre west facing lot in the heart of Ambleside this unique property has a secondary secured access off of 19th Street perfect for a possible second garage? coach house? boat storage…there are an infinite number of possibilities!

Beautiful interior details and modern luxuries make the home an exceptional place to enjoy leisure time. A stunning 21’ entry hall leads you past a cozy living room, pretty formal dining room, private office an into the incredible great room, kitchen and breakfast area with large windows that allow for ample natural light and open onto a lovely covered patio that overlooks the stunning yard.

Up the grand staircase to the master suite with two walk-in closets, a deluxe ensuite and a private lounge. There are three spacious addition ensuited bedrooms plus a secondary laundry also on this floor.

Down has everything you could ask for – a media area, bar, rec room, wine cellar, fifth bedroom, gym and an enclosed swimming pool that opens out to the backyard …absolutely perfect for adults and children alike!

With nearly limitless opportunities for enjoying quiet family time, or working in the tranquility of a pristine environment this home is an exceptional find and truly has it all!

Welcome to our video listing the Top 8 Old Money Luxury Bags!

The old money aesthetic is not about imitating the mega wealthy of today, is about a classic and elegant style that is timeless. Here on this video I’ll show you 8 amazing bags that are definitely old money, and are so understated you might not know.

These are bags that are very quiet and unknown to the masses, only those in the know can recognize these bags. I kept out of this list bags from Hermès and Chanel, not because they aren’t old money, but because at this point I believe they are recognizable even to those outside of the fashion world.

I went to my friend's house, who moved to Pangyowon Village in Pangyo, to play, and looked around Unjung-dong for a while, right next to Gyeomsagyeomsa Temple. items.Video_Title: HOUSE TOUR | Quiet Luxury Farmhouse Kitchen at this Coastal Compound Estate
items.Video_Description:
This week @DesignerHomeTours we are exploring the 28,000-square-foot main house (as featured in Architectural Digest) of a multi-building compound dwelling along the coast of the Eastern Maryland seaboard.  Acclaimed Architect Cathy Purple Cherry of Purple Cherry Architects walked us through the expansive property of her longtime client, which consists of an impressive nine structures, four of which were pre-existing, and notably entails the main house, party barn, carriage house, pottery studio, greenhouse, and boat house. Fans of Nancy Meyers interiors know it is one of the top interior design trends 2022, and this home is a prime example of coastal grandmother decor with white millwork, classic Americana design and breathtaking landscape views. The gorgeous, lush, and significant landscape doubles as a fully operable farm with striking views of seemingly infinite pastures.  The full build-out and renovation spanned over the course of a decade and functions today as the client's family’s weekend getaway where they host holidays, parties, and events.   The overall look and style of this estate is a balanced mixture of neo-colonial, transitional, and coastal, with a touch of organic modern with a multi-layered textural neutral color palette that thematically shows up throughout the structures.  The family-oriented design that sits carefully within the crafted architectural details makes this home one to truly remember. #stealthwealth #quietluxury

items.Video_Title: British luxury bags - traditional to quirky (including Royal favourites) - are they worth buying?
items.Video_Description:
Asprey (with a Royal Warrant from HRH the Prince of Wales), Launer, Mulberry, Aspinal of London and Anya Hindmarsh are all brands favoured by various members of the Royal Family from the Queen herself (Launer) to Kate, Duchess of Cambridge, wife of Prince William (Mulberry, Aspinal and Anya Hindmarsh).

They are high quality and in the main more reasonably priced than the big luxury French and Italian fashion houses.  They carry their branding quietly and many bear the hallmarks of elegant good taste.  

I have the Mulberry Darley small shoulder bag in quilted leather - a look alike to the attractive Chanel Business Affinity (but a fraction of the price and much better made!); the Aspinal of London Mayfair bag, size mini; one of the famous Anya Hindmarch clutches; and a quirky Lulu Guinness Oyster bag bought as a gift for someone.

Please let me know what you think of these brands and if you own or would consider buying one of them! x

Welcome to our video listing the Top 10 Quiet Luxury Bags!

When it comes to luxury there are basically two types of brands, the loud and the quiet ones. We all know the loud ones; they are always on your face with big logos and marketing campaigns, like Louis Vuitton and Gucci for example. We love them, but if you believe that less is more then you are definitely a fan of quiet luxury.

Quiet luxury brands offer products with subtle or no markings. Quiet luxury is not centered around the logo, or showing off wealth and status, instead, it’s all about the beauty, quality, and craftsmanship of the product. 

Here I’ll show you 10 bags that perfectly represent quiet luxury, I’m sure you will love them! Some bags on this list are pretty well known but that doesn’t mean it isn’t quiet luxury. 

If you would like to know more about quiet luxury make sure to check my video about the top 10 quiet luxury brands!
